{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qinfeng-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qinfeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-qinfeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·秦風·009.1", "text_original": "我送舅氏，曰至渭陽。何以贈之，路車乘黃。\n我送舅氏，悠悠我思。何以贈之，瓊瑰玉佩。", "text_normalized": "我送舅氏，曰至渭陽。何以贈之，路車乘黃。\n我送舅氏，悠悠我思。何以贈之，瓊瑰玉佩。", "notes": "渭陽 Chinese poem 1."}
